{"tid":1728042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"終於知咩係真愛，就係知佢有男朋友既時候都仲係祝福佢，忍唔住爆喊左","createTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:46:48.000Z","uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00111b80320d845048cb1a499fcdcccb29fd4f68","tid":1728042,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"原來就算我同佢完全唔識，仲要異地，但係只要係網上面睇到佢既相就會有番晒動力同笑得好傻<br />\n點解你咁快就有男朋友阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一直以來既目標都係為左將來可以娶你，點解阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photo.polylulu.com.tw/photo/photo/ow/95070073-A23-05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.polylulu.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fphoto%2Fow%2F95070073-A23-05.jpg&h=93d5bc31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://photo.polylulu.com.tw/photo/photo/ow/92260064-A42-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.polylulu.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fphoto%2Fow%2F92260064-A42-02.jpg&h=f601210f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://photo.polylulu.com.tw//Photo/PDImg/93070036/93070036-A42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.polylulu.com.tw%2F%2FPhoto%2FPDImg%2F93070036%2F93070036-A42.jpg&h=423813cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://photo.polylulu.com.tw/photo/photo/ow/92310589-A98-05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.polylulu.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fphoto%2Fow%2F92310589-A98-05.jpg&h=87bfa95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這天聽說妳很好<br />\n得到美滿吧<br />\n快將與那個他 成家<br />\n冒失的妳 由他看顧<br />\n此時我哪需記掛<br />\n<br />\n記得妳最愛冬天<br />\n他都愛上吧<br />\n與他過最暖的寒假<br />\n熱戀的你們<br />\n幸福得太像童話<br />\n<br />\n當他掀起了新一篇<br />\n給妳新轉變<br />\n沒有遺憾在後 望未來是直線<br />\n終於妳的悲觀 給歡笑聲感染<br />\n這也是最美好的發展<br />\n<br />\n我這樣討厭 他完美如此 能共妳好好地相處<br />\n哪會像我們 將吵架當玩意 沒法挽手一輩子<br />\n最掛念的妳 悲劇已停止 無用再傷心另一次<br />\n妳我未有幸 一起說聲願意 但這位跟妳可以<br />\n<br />\n祝褔聲想妳都聽到<br />\n可記得當年<br />\n是我們沒毅力 漸漸行漸漸遠<br />\n請謹記這一天 多點信心走前<br />\n再也別怕那些小雨點<br />\n<br />\n我這樣討厭 他完美如此 能共妳好好地相處<br />\n哪會像我們 將吵架當玩意 沒法挽手一輩子<br />\n最掛念的妳 悲劇已停止 無用再傷心另一次<br />\n妳我未有幸 一起說聲願意 但這位 跟妳 可以<br />\n讓我都偷說一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a3f97a9bd96514b5d83b9b2930ea1f2484a1c7","tid":1728042,"uid":136738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\